OL,6,FA group of men in Gaza, holding a
OL,7,Fwhite flag, told ITV News they wanted
OL,8,Fto rescue their family members -
OL,9,Fminutes later one was shot dead as
OL,10,FJohn Irvine reports
OL,12,FThe English-speaking man lamented the
OL,13,Ffact that having fled Gaza City when
OL,14,Fthis war began, the family were now
OL,15,Frunning away again, this time
OL,16,Fabandoning to head for Rafah.
OL,18,FTheir attempts to escape the war have
OL,19,Ftaken them from the top of the to the
OL,20,Fbottom.
