OL,6,FThey are among hundreds of thousands
OL,7,Fof people hemmed in, with their backs
OL,8,Fto the Egyptian border and the IDF
OL,9,Fbearing down.
OL,11,F"Nowhere is safe in Gaza," he told a
OL,12,Fcameraman working for ITV News.
OL,14,F"Everywhere you find the Israeli Army.
OL,15,FThey shoot at us at home, in any
OL,16,Fbuilding and in the street."
