OL,6,FHe had no way of knowing just how
OL,7,Fprophetic his words were because
OL,8,Fminutes later, the cameraman filmed an
OL,9,Finnocent civilian being shot dead in
OL,10,Fthe street.
OL,12,FThe cameraman noticed Ramzi Abu
OL,13,FSahloul because he was among a group
OL,14,Fof five males standing still, their
OL,15,Fhands up, one of them brandishing a
OL,16,Fwhite flag.
OL,18,FSpeaking on camera, Mr Abu Sahloul
OL,19,Fsaid they were trying to reach his
OL,20,Fmother and brother to escort them out
OL,21,Fof harm's way.
