OL,6,FBillowing plumes of smoke and the
OL,7,Fsound of gunfire indicated that combat
OL,8,Fwas taking place nearby.
OL,10,FThe interview complete, the cameraman
OL,11,Fwalked away.
OL,13,FHe then turned to get one last picture
OL,14,Fof the group when suddenly, there was
OL,15,Fa sharp loud volley of shots.
OL,17,FThe five started to run, but within
OL,18,Fseconds Mr Abu Sahloul collapsed on
OL,19,Fthe ground.
