OL,6,FHe'd been shot in the chest. One of
OL,7,Fthe men placed the flag on his wounds.
OL,9,FBetween them, they lifted him and as
OL,10,Fthey carried him away you could
OL,11,Fclearly make out the white flag
OL,12,Fturning red.
OL,14,FThe 51-year-old husband and father
OL,15,Fwasn't moving and it seems his death
OL,16,Fwas almost instantaneous.
