OL,6,FAs they tried to carry him to safety,
OL,7,Fthere was the sound of more gunfire
OL,8,Fand the whoosh of a bullet passing
OL,9,Fnearby suggested the group was still
OL,10,Fbeing targeted.
OL,12,FEventually they got the body to a
OL,13,Fsafer place, where his wife, his
OL,14,Fwidow, began to wail and mourn her
OL,15,Floss.
OL,17,FMr Abu Sahloul sold children's clothes
OL,18,Ffor a living.
